reviewText: The Donut Repair Club is always fun for the little ones.  Duncan is funny and the songs are cute and singable.  The Donut Man always has a good theme to communicate, too.

This is a great video for kids.  Great tunes sung by young kids.  Moral story line.  Grandkids from 1 to 10 watch at same time seeing something  different.  If your kids like animals this is the video for them.
